31#include "mech_locl.h"
32
33GSSAPI_LIB_FUNCTION OM_uint32 GSSAPI_LIB_CALL
34gss_indicate_mechs(OM_uint32 *minor_status,
35 gss_OID_set *mech_set)
36{
37 struct _gss_mech_switch *m;
38 OM_uint32 major_status;
39 gss_OID_set set;
40 size_t i;
41
42 _gss_load_mech();
43
44 major_status = gss_create_empty_oid_set(minor_status, mech_set);
45 if (major_status)
46 return (major_status);
47
48 /* XXX We ignore ENOMEM from gss_add_oid_set_member() */
49 HEIM_SLIST_FOREACH(m, &_gss_mechs, gm_link) {
50 if (m->gm_mech.gm_indicate_mechs) {
51 major_status = m->gm_mech.gm_indicate_mechs(
52 minor_status, &set);
53 if (major_status)
54 continue;
55 for (i = 0; i < set->count; i++)
56 gss_add_oid_set_member(
57 minor_status, &set->elements[i], mech_set);
58 gss_release_oid_set(minor_status, &set);
59 } else {
60 gss_add_oid_set_member(
61 minor_status, &m->gm_mech_oid, mech_set);
62 }
63 }
64
65 *minor_status = 0;
66 return (GSS_S_COMPLETE);
67}
